highlights.text: “Heaven” by Avicii is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #13.
Billie Eilish has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “bad guy” is the highest at #2.
“Tough Love (feat. Agnes, Vargas & Lagola)” by Avicii, Agnes, and Vargas & Lagola is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 92 spots at #102.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 127 weeks straight.
